@109 = ~Friendly

Range: 0
Duration: 1 turn
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: The caster
Saving Throw: None

The Charlatan uses <PRO_HISHER> charm to get a boost of 5 points to Charisma.~
@110 = ~Pretend~
@111 = ~Pretend

